      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はーい、みなさん、ここが京都の鴨川です",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "鴨川は、京文化を語る上で外せない名所なんですよ～",
      "startTime": 5.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "夏になると、子供が川遊びして涼んでますし",
      "startTime": 11.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "七夕のお祭りもやるんですよ～",
      "startTime": 15.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "カップルで並んで座るんが、定番のデートやし\n恋してる方は、チェックして下さい～",
      "startTime": 22.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ほな、一緒に歩きながら眺めて行きましょか",
      "startTime": 25.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3832.9068391000014,
          "startTime": 29.0662401724
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（簡単な台本しかないのに）",
      "startTime": 30.2483589172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "（流れるようなトークだな……さすがだ）",
      "startTime": 32.2150255839,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.6666666,
          "startTime": 37.2816922505
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この辺りは、春やと桜が凄く綺麗なんです",
      "startTime": 38.1483589172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うちも小さい時は、母とお花見に来たことあります\nめっちゃ楽しかったなぁ",
      "startTime": 47.4816922505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "うちの母は女優さんやから、変装してたんですけど\nうちがあんまり大声で話すんで、周りの人に注目されて",
      "startTime": 53.5150255839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すぐバレて、その後大変やったなぁ",
      "startTime": 58.6483589172,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2366.6666666999986,
          "startTime": 61.0150255839
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "くすっ、今となってはいい思い出ですわぁ",
      "startTime": 62.1816922505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（芸能人ならではの思い出トークか……）\n（視聴者が喜びそうな話題を、さりげなく入れてきた）",
      "startTime": 69.9816922505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（ライブのMCでトークがうまいのは知っていたけど）\n（鈴村さんの仕事は、安心して見ていられるな）",
      "startTime": 76.6150255839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ほな、もうちょっと進んでみましょか\nこの先には、うちがよく行った商店街があります",
      "startTime": 83.9816922505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "今流行りの昭和レトロっぽい雰囲気のお店が\n結構あるんですよ～",
      "startTime": 91.6150255839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "これから、そっちのぞいてみましょか",
      "startTime": 93.7483589172,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4000,
          "startTime": 97.7483589172
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
